Controllers

Interface MenuInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BuyTicketController, DiscountReqController, HomeScreenController, walletController

    public interface MenuInterface
    tento interface implementuje kazdy controller ktory ovlada pouzivatelsku cast programu z kazdej sceny kde sa vie dostat bezny pouzivatel sa da preklikat na ine sceny, preto ho musi mat kazdy takyto controller.
